ğŸ“ Dataset Files Description

This repository includes three preprocessed CSV files derived from the IU Chest X-Ray dataset. These files are used for training, validation, and testing of the image captioning models.

ğŸ“„ Files Included
      File Name	Purpose
      Train_Data.csv	  Used for model training
      CV_Data.csv	      Used for validation / hyperparameter tuning
      Test_Data.csv	      Used for final evaluation

ğŸ“Š CSV File Structure

Each CSV file follows the same structure:

      Column Name	                     Description
      person_id               Unique identifier for each patient or image pair
      image1	              Filename of the first chest X-ray image (frontal or lateral view)
      image2	              Filename of the second chest X-ray image (paired view or same image)
      report	              Cleaned radiology caption (Findings + Impression)


